                <ion-icon name="play-sharp"></ion-icon>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="pattern">* * *</div>
          <div class="copy">
            <p>
              DID SHE DO IT? <br /> A woman is suspected of her husbandâ€™s murder,
              and their blind son faces a moral dilemma as the sole witness.
